## Why Lanolips — factual differentiators
- Powered by ultra-pure lanolin that is uniquely semi-occlusive and semi-permeable: it helps prevent moisture loss while letting skin self-hydrate, and can hold up to twice its weight in water.
- 100% natural with zero petroleum; free from parabens, sulfates and artificial fragrance.
- Cruelty-free (Leaping Bunny certified via third-party verifier Provenance) and vegetarian.
- Clinically and dermatologically tested; safe during pregnancy, while nursing, and for newborns.
- The 101 Ointment holds the National Eczema Association (NEA) Seal of Acceptance.
- Multipurpose value: one balm can replace several single-use products.
- Founder-led, female-owned and Australian. Lanolin is sourced ethically as a by-product of annual wool washing — sheep are shorn for their welfare regardless, and are not harmed for the ingredient.

## Key product
- 101 Ointment Multipurpose Superbalm
